| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5084 — Recovery Inhibition (cactus)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 0506d2f9-26fe-5be2-8ef6-265e43aeeeab"
